Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,TERIMA KASIH: {\c&Hffff00&}gendhutz, Ibnu triawan, Seseorang,\NSophie Lengkong, Penonton miawaug, Arjuna Plantagenet, Lk21.de{\c}\Natas SUPPORTNYA di: {\c&H8080ff&}trakteer.id/broth3rmaxSUB
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.44,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,berikan SUPPORT di:\N{\c&H8080ff&}trakteer.id/broth3rmaxSUB
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayo Layla, biar ayah dengar suara merdumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayolah, demi ayahmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kau bikin kepalaku puyeng.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kalian semua.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,terjemahan broth3r{\i1}max{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Selamatkan dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anak-anak...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,tunggu disini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanya di {\c&H8080ff&}AYUKBET{\c}, Menang dapat {\c&H00ff80&}REBATE 1,3%{\c}\Ndan kalah juga dapat {\c&H00ff80&}CASHBACK 5%{\c}\NCari kami di GOOGLE : AYUKBET
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kita tahu sekaranglah saatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kita periksa dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelan-pelan, buka sedikit saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Apa dia sudah bangkit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Katakan, dia bangkit atau belum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Alhamdulillah.
